Nordiansyah Nasrie Chief Operating Officer Appointed 0h 72 November 2074

Mr Nordiansyah Nasrie is the Chief Operating Officer of the Group. He is responslble for the overall operations of the Group and ensuring that its operational activities are in accordance with policies, goals and objectives of the Group. He joined the Group as the director of Rinjani, a subsidiary of the Company, in 2008. Prior to joining the Group, Nordiansyah Nasrie was appointed as a director in various energy companies including PT Kutai Etam Petroleum and PT Kutai Energy Resources. He is currently a director of PT Energy Indonesia Resources, PT Faisal Sampurna, PT Kembang Jahggut Sawtt Sejahtera, PT Muara Kaman Sawit Sejahtera and PT Kota Bangun Sawit Sejahtera. He is also the commisstoner of PT Pancaran Berkat Adidaya. Nordiahsyah Nasrie graduated with a Dtploma of Academy Hotet and Tourism from Internattonal College Bandung. Nordiansyah Nasri also graduated wtth a Magister of Law from University Merdeka Malang.
